Image(lacrosse 1.jpg, photo by Elise Kane, thumbnail)   Womens lacrosse exists at UC Davis as both a Division I NCAA team and as a highly competitive club sport. More information about the NCAA team can be found at http://www.ucdavisaggies.com/sports/wlacros/ucdawlacrosbody.html. More information about the club team can be found at http://campusrecreation.ucdavis.edu/sport_clubs/clubs_womenslacrosse.php
